A vast African savanna at dusk with thousands of glowing fireflies forming an interconnected mesh pattern across the sky, each tiny light connected to others by faint luminescent threads creating a living network. In the foreground, a lone acacia tree silhouetted against the orange and purple gradient sky, while the firefly swarm above mimics the structure of a distributed computing network, pulsing with coordinated bioluminescent signals. The scene blends organic nature with technological undertones, suggesting collective intelligence emerging from countless small connected nodes. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, dreamy atmospheric lighting, and that signature sense of magical wonder found in nature.
